    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers straightforward value for a buyer who wants dependable basic transportation without a big upfront cost. It shows its age cosmetically and is best suited for someone practical who appreciates an affordable entry point, a project opportunity, or a reliable extra vehicle. Priced to reflect its condition while still delivering solid value.",
