    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car that\u2019s ready for someone handy or anyone after an affordable runabout/project. It\u2019s not perfect and it shows its age, but it\u2019s a complete vehicle with plenty of potential for the right buyer. If you\u2019re looking for a cheap way into a car and don\u2019t mind giving it some TLC, this could be a great fit. Priced fairly, sold as-is, and worth a look if you want value without spending a fortune.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Driver-grade project with solid bones and plenty of potential. The powertrain pulls through the rev range, the chassis feels planted, and it has the kind of analog character enthusiasts look for. Not a showroom car, but a usable platform for someone who wants a budget-friendly entry point with mechanical personality and room to improve. A straightforward, honest car that can be enjoyed as-is while you sort the cosmetic and deferred items over time.",
      "price": 7950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
