      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn character you can\u2019t fake\u2014a seasoned companion with plenty of story left to tell. It\u2019s an ideal fit for someone who wants an inexpensive set of wheels, a hands-on project, or a practical backup vehicle with personality. There\u2019s a certain charm in the way it shows its miles: unpolished, approachable, and ready for its next chapter with the right owner. If you appreciate potential over pretense, this one offers a budget-friendly way to get behind the wheel and make it your own.",
